  "method": [
    "Preheat the oven to 350°F.",
    "Line a baking sheet with parchment paper and set aside.",
    "Add the mashed banana and peanut butter to a large bowl and mix well. Add the applesauce, flour, hempseed, and vanilla. Mix well. Stir in the oatmeal and dates.",
    "Drop cookie dough, 1 heaping tablespoon at a time and 2 inches apart, onto the prepared baking sheet. Flatten with the back of a fork. Bake cookies for 25 minutes.",
    "Remove from the oven and let the cookies cool 5 minutes, then move to a cooling rack."
